{"tid":331511,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"（勸喻溝緊人既巴絲）若要被愛，請先自愛","createTime":"2017-07-22T08:50:01.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-22T08:50:01.000Z","uid":101103,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"03fc93cad8abfa3726e32fe2295854fbb9ebe36a","tid":331511,"uid":101103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T08:50:01.000Z","msg":"相識雖然係一種緣分<br />\n但人地對你不瞅不睬，日日等住人覆，無晒尊嚴，最後仲賤過地底泥咁去搵人，為咩呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n勸奉咁多位，如果搞到自己咁難受，就不如放手啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n總會搵到一個大家都珍惜對方既人，未搵到只到未遇到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後一句，大家一齊加油啦"}]}